**Output Format and Translation Rules:**

*   For in-text quote marks, always use \".
*   Convert imperial units to metric approximately in the descriptive texts, favoring natural-sounding Polish expressions (e.g., "około metra," "nieco ponad metr") over overly precise conversions unless context demands it. For the mechanical contexts, leave feet.
*   Maintain HTML input as HTML and translate the contents.
